{"service_name": "Information Assurance and CLAS Consultancy", "service_id": "4791359131090944", "company_name": "MASS Consultants Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     MASS Consultants Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Information Assurance and CLAS Consultancy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Our team of IA &amp; CLAS consultants are multi-disciplined, experienced in risk assessment, accreditation and IA auditing.  Practised in interpreting and implementing the requirements of HMG, Defence and the wider public sector; ensuring information assets and ICT systems are afforded proportionate protection in line with business and security requirements.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Membership of the CESG Listed Advisor Scheme (CLAS).\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Information Security Risk Assessment and Risk Treatment Planning.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business / Privacy Impact Assessment and security policy framework compliance.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ISO 27001 auditing and implementation.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     High quality RMADS production, policy development and accreditation support.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IT Health Check, Cyber Essentials Plus and Vulnerability Assessment.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CCP roles \u2013 SIRA, IA Auditor, ITSO.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IA and security training and awareness.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Continuity Planning.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Design, implementation and support of secure system architectures.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Helping businesses demonstrate Information Assurance Maturity.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Agility and flexibility, use experienced professionals without high resourcing requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduce information security risks and potential for reputational damage.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stakeholder confidence, knowing information risk is managed effectively.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provide robust risk and accreditation evidence to SIRO and Accreditor.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stakeholder and Accreditor confidence in technical compliance and security.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enhance business and individuals knowledge and awareness.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enable protection of business operational status and reputation.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3740 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92711/4791359131090944-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92711/4791359131090944-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n    